	(21, 'B-08/2023/1', 'demo', NULL, 'demo', 'demouser@demo.com', '9459874826', 'India', NULL, NULL, 'I', NULL, '<h3 style="text-transform: uppercase;" align="center">Memorandum of Understanding</h3>\r\n<p>This Memorandum of Understanding is entered on 19th of August 2023 at Dehradun Between M/s. <strong>demo</strong> having its registered office at (1st party) and <strong> The Government of Uttarakhand (2nd party)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong> </strong> where in M/s. <strong>demo</strong> wishes to establish the following project(s) in Uttarakhand</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class="project-table" style="border: 1px solid #000000;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="border: 1px solid #000000;">\r\n<th style="border: 1px solid #000000;">Project Brief</th>\r\n<th style="border: 1px solid #000000;">Location</th>\r\n<th style="border: 1px solid #000000;">Proposed Minimum Investment (INR)</th>\r\n<th style="border: 1px solid #000000;">Direct Employment Generation (Number)</th>\r\n<th style="border: 1px solid #000000;">Proposed commencement date of production</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="border: 1px solid #000000;">\r\n<td style="border: 1px solid #000000;">The Single Window Clearance System Portal is a single window facilitation mechanism for investors The portal is a medium of information for investors on Government policies incentive schemes and the availability of infrastructure It provides manuals to help investors to understand the application process for proposed investment projects The portal will also facilitate different stakeholder departments to process applications by investors and approve them online It also aims to build a centralized repository of sector wise investments in the State and Government policies and ultimately to deliver to investors a high quality and responsive service</td>\r\n<td style="border: 1px solid #000000;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="border: 1px solid #000000;">80000000</td>\r\n<td style="border: 1px solid #000000;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="border: 1px solid #000000;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Government of Uttarakhand would facilitate M/s. <strong>demo</strong> to obtain necessary permissions/registrations/approvals/clearances etc. from the concerned Departments/Agencies/Authorities of the State, as per the existing policies/rules and regulations of the State Government.</p>\r\n<p>This Memorandum of Understanding is made to facilitate M/s. <strong>demo</strong> for the establishment of the aforesaid project in Uttarakhand in a time-bound manner.</p>\r\n<p>This MOU indicates the intention of the investor in brief about the proposed industry and the possible facilitation to be extended by the State Government and shall remain valid only for a maximum period of 12 (twelve) months from the date of entering into MOU unless otherwise extended by the second party. No separate notice will be required to be issued for this.</p>\r\n<p>First Party will have to submit the Common Application Form (CAF) through the Single Window Approval Portal for all necessary and statutory approvals and clearances prior to the commencement of construction and production. The CAF submission should be within the period of validity of this MOU.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<table class="signature">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>For and on behalf of M/s</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class="signatory"><img style="width: 25mm;" src="../../uploads/logo/sign/test_inv_sign.jpg" alt="">\r\n<p style="text-align: center; padding-right: 10px;">(Authorised Signatory)</p>\r\n<p>Name: demo</p>\r\n<p>Designation:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Address:</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<table class="signature">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>For and on behalf of Government of Uttarakhand</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class="signatory"><img style="width: 25mm;" src="../../uplo