	(904, 'A-11/2023/276', 'Piyush chaurasia ', NULL, 'Piyush chaurasia ', 'piyushchaurasia2512@gmail.com', '9453002285', 'India', 'MEDIUM', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\r\nFBP is a company that develops mobile applications to solve student problems and provide free notes and question papers for B.tech, class 9th to 12th. The company\'s mission is to help students succeed in their studies by providing them with the resources they need to learn effectively.\r\n\r\nFBP\'s mobile applications offer a variety of features that can help students improve their academic performance, including:\r\n\r\nFree notes and question papers: FBP\'s mobile applications provide students with access to a vast library of free notes and question papers for a wide range of subjects. This can be a valuable resource for students who are struggling with their studies or who simply want to supplement their learning with additional materials.\r\nInteractive learning tools: FBP\'s mobile applications include a variety of interactive learning tools, such as quizzes, flashcards, and practice problems. These tools can help students to test their understanding of course material and identify areas where they need additional help.\r\nPersonalized learning plans: FBP\'s mobile applications can create personalized learning plans for each student. These plans are based on the student\'s individual needs and goals, and they can help students to stay on track with their studies.', NULL, 10000000, 'Individual', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A', 'S', NULL, NULL, NULL, 814, 'SUBMITTED', NULL, 'N', 'N', 'Y', '2023-11-18 17:28:03', NULL, 'I', NULL, NULL, 'N', 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-18 11:58:03', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL),
