	(906, 'D-11/2023/82', 'Sevozone Energies and Fertilizers Pvt Ltd', NULL, 'Jaivil Rana', 'info@sevozone.com', '9319061936', 'India', 'MEDIUM', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dear Sir,\r\n\r\nGreetings of the day,\r\n\r\nYou may be aware that, Sevozone is a young organization formed by agriculturist and registered as MSME (UDYAM-CH-01-0009480) & Corporate Member of Indian Biogas Association and involved into the manufacturing of Bio Gas, Bio-CNG with strategic relationship with Indian Oil Corporation Ltd. (IOCL – A Govt. of India Enterprises) for supply of Bio-CNG at their CNG supplied to CNG Stations through Cascade/ Cylinder or can be delivered in the adjacent Gas Grid.\r\n\r\nBio Gas business as green fuel is having a lot of potential for Biogas generation from different types of organic wastes & its sale to PSU Oil Marketing Companies and own retail gas outlets . Our aim is to be a major contributor for the value addition of Bio Gas by utilizing it for BIO-CNG as Automotive Fuel and Bio Fertilizer.\r\n\r\nOur group is in process to set up 04 Compressed Biogas Plant (CBG / CNG) Plants with 28 TPD CBG Plants with the investment of Rs. 190 Crores in the state of Uttar Pradesh under UP Bio Energy Policy 2022.\r\n\r\nSimilarly we are also interested to setup mixed Feed based (Cow Dung & SugarCane Pressmud, Agriculture Residue) 02 Nos of Compressed Biogas & Bio-Fertilizer Plans (6 TPD each) in Tehsil Roorkee and Rudrapur with total investment of Rs.  85 Crores.\r\n\r\nNeed state government support on long term Raw Material Tie-ups (Sugarcane Pressmud) with Cooperative Sugar Mills & Land.\r\n\r\nKindly facilitate us for signing an Investment MOU under Uttrakhand Global Investor Summit 2023.\r\n\r\nThanks & Regards', NULL, 850000000, 'Organization', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'D', 'S', NULL, NULL, NULL, 816, 'SUBMITTED', NULL,