	(907, 'D-11/2023/83', 'Far N Beyond Sustainable LLP', NULL, 'Jyoti Swarup', 'jyotiswarup03@gmail.com', '9891798383', 'India', 'MEDIUM', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Project Concept note “Wine Panda at” Garhi Cantt Dehradoon by Jyoti Swarup\r\n\r\n                                                                                 \r\n\r\nThe Proposed project is to develop a wine wellness destination and center of excellence for knowledge sharing for wellness of Body, Mind and Soul inculcating Indian family values, Joy of Giving, Respect for Elderly and tribute to the fallen soldier.\r\nIn the proposed facility following shall be provided:\r\n1.	Special concession to the families who bring their aged senior citizen parents with them.\r\n2.	Free stay of War widows and their immediate family members for a duration of two days and subsequent special concessions.\r\n3.	Free access to wine hobby makers, Researchers, Doctors, Wine Enthusiasts, Visiting faculties and like. Wine club\r\n4.	To provide wine tasting and winery tourism for health benefits.\r\n5.	Personal signature bottling and warehouse.\r\n6.	Service points for Motorhomes and Caravans free of cost. \r\n\r\nAdjacent Haridwar is a spiritual destination where devotees converge to know their heredity lineage through Pandas who keep records of vanshavali and records of their forefathers visit at Ganga with their signatures or thumbprints. A proposed wine cellar is part of this resort hotel where bottled wine shall be kept with signature on the label of bottle.\r\nGarhi is located half hours drive away from Haridwar, connected with rail, excellent road and air from Dehradoon.\r\nTargeted Professionals: Army veterans, Doctors, Lawyers, CA, Engineers, Architects, Teachers, Lecturers, Professionals, Business Men and above all Foreign Tourists \r\n1.	Project Components:\r\nLiberal use of Quartz stone and Crystals, Wines, Ayurvedic massage, Bamboo, and sunshine which are believed to be having curing properties and attributes.\r\