tric (Hyklin Skyline Electric Private Limited)</p>\r\n<p>Sahy Electric (Hyklin Skyline Electric Private Limited) is in the business of isetting up, operating and maintaining EV charging infrastructure. Sahy is a startup Uttarakhand registered entity and eligible for pilot projects with the State government as per the Startup Policy. Sahy intents to initially invest Rs. 50 crore to setup EV charging infrastructure in the Cities of Dehradun, Haridwar, Mussoorie, Haldwani, Rishikesh, Nainital, Landsdowne etc. and operates on the following models: 1)Outright Sale of Chargers with software maintanence contract on a revenue sharing basis 2)Setup of own chargers with 10 year agreement alongwith right to setup information and advertisement screens in the licensed area. Sahy offers to invest in setup of EV charging infrasuch as fast chargers for cars and buses, slow chargers for cars, buses, 2W &amp; 3W alongwith battery swapping stations. The desired locations and pilots are sought for the following locations: 1)Transport Department - ISBT terminals for setup of fast and slow chargers for cars and Buses. Battery swapping stations for 3 wheelers and 2 wheelers 2)Tourism Department - Setup of chargers at all UKTDC guesthouses and hotels shall increase the footfall of EV users at these locations by providing them with greater visibility 3)Govt Parking lots - We offer to setup the complete range of charging solutions here for EVs such as slow and fast chargers, battery swapping stations etc. 4) Large Govt offices - In order to increase the adoption and ease of use of EVs by government we can setup chargers at all these locations 5)State &amp; National Highways - Charging stations after every 50 KM range will ensure that a Uttarakhand based startup is the front contender for setting a brand and a benchmark in highway charging Based on the amount of contracts recieved the investment can be increased 10 fold.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; padding: 10px 5px; border: 1px solid #000000;">more than 150</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; padding: 10px 5px; border: 1px solid #000000;">50</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; padding: 10px 5px; border: 1px solid #000000;">250 directly and indirectly</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; padding: 10px 5px; border: 1px solid #000000;">180 days from the date of contract</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 24px; ;margin-left: 50px; margin-left: 50px;">Government of Uttarakhand would facilitate the investor to obtain all necessary approvals/clearances for commencement of the project. The MoU shall remain valid for a period of 12 months.</p>\r\n<p><br><br><br></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%; ;margin-left: 50px; margin-left: 50px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<table style="width: 300px; height: 300px; border-radius: 5px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 20px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><!-- <input type="text" style="border:none;border-bottom:2px solid #000000;background-color:transparent;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;width:250px;"> -->\r\n<p style="margin-left: 3px; width: 106%; height: 1px; background-color: #000;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 20px;">On behalf of<br>Hyklin Skyline Electric Private Limited,<br>Aseem Gupta</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<table style="width: 300px; height: 300px; border-radius: 5px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 20px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><!-- <input type="text" style="border:none;border-bottom:2px solid #000000;background-color:transparent;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;width:300px"> -->\r\n<p style="margin-left: 3px; width: 106%; height: 1px; background-color: #000;">&nbsp;</p>\