	(941, 'D-11/2023/92', 'ShivOm Dayal Energies Haridwar Pvt Ltd', NULL, 'Ashish Ahuja', 'info@shivomdayalenergies.com', '9717806209', 'India', 'MEDIUM', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Our Company ShivOm Dayal Energies Haridwar (P) Ltd. is setting up a 18 TPD. CBG (Compressed Biogas) Plant at Laksar, Dist - Haridwar. Our company is investing Rs 65 Cr. in this project as well as providing direct and indirect employment to over 250 people. The proposed CBG plant aligns with the goals of the SATAT scheme, focusing on utilizing organic waste for the production of clean and affordable biogas. \r\n\r\nA significant aspect of our proposal is the production of CBG for use in the transportation sector. This aligns with the SATAT scheme\'s objective of promoting the use of compressed biogas as a sustainable and affordable alternative to conventional fuels. Our project emphasizes the economic viability of CBG production, creating a win-win situation for both the community and stakeholders. \r\nThe Benefits of the project include:\r\n?  Reduction in Greenhouse Gas (GHG) emissions, thereby reducing Pollution\r\n?  Saving on foreign currency and lowering bills of natural gas.\r\n?  Socio-Economic Upliftment of rural areas\r\n?  Formation of Green Economy and investment of rupees ?65 Crores? in the state.\r\n?  Waste Management: converts organic waste into energy\r\n?  Renewable Energy Target:s Contributes to national and state renewable energy goals.\r\n?  Energy Security Enhancement: Utilizes local resources, reducing dependence on imported fuels.\r\n?  Waste-to-Wealth Initiatives: Addresses waste management challenges, promoting circular economy.\r\n\r\nThe Plant is already under construction and we envision commercial production to commence by January, 2024. \r\nWe request you to provide support in the form of:\r\nSigning of MoU at upcoming Investors Summit\r\nReimbursement of SGST, Electricity duty exemption, Interest subsidy and other benefits of Large Projects as per the Uttarakhand Investment policy\r\nWe look forward to your earliest communication in the matter; we shall provide all the necessary information, as may be sought by you.\r\n', NULL, 650000000, 'Organization', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'D', 'S', NULL, NULL, NULL, 831, 'SUBMITTED', NULL, 'N', 'N', 'Y', '2023-11-22 17:01:27', NULL, 'I', NULL, 831, 'N', 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-22 11:31:27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL),
