igns.\r\n\r\nJob creation and skill development in advanced technology sectors.\r\nContribution to the local economy through business and technology partnerships.\r\nCommitment to environmental sustainability in operations and construction.\r\nThis investment proposal for an AI, Robotics, and Drone assembly unit represents a significant opportunity for technological and economic advancement in Uttarakhand. The project is aligned with the vision of the State Government of Uttarakhand for promoting innovation, sustainable development, and economic growth in the region.\r\n', NULL, 50000000, 'Organization', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'B', 'S', NULL, NULL, NULL, 836, 'SUBMITTED', NULL, 'N', 'N', 'Y', '2023-11-22 19:39:43', NULL, 'I', NULL, 836, 'N', 'N', NULL, NULL, 'MoU-UKGIS-0002', NULL, '2023-11-22 14:11:39', NULL, '2023-11-22 14:09:43', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL),
