	(958, 'E-11/2023/287', 'Ecoveda Greens', NULL, 'Chirayu Magan', 'chirayu@ecovedagreens.com', '9012011007', 'India', 'MEDIUM', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Intent to Invest in Uttarakhand - Comprehensive Infrastructure and Tourism Development Project\r\n\r\nRespected Sir/Madam,\r\n\r\nI am writing on behalf of EcoVeda Greens, a company committed to sustainable development, with a vision to transform the landscape of Kota in Rishikesh, Uttarakhand.\r\n\r\nWe have recently invested in 40 acres (800 Nali) of land in Kota, Rishikesh, with plans to develop the area into a thriving hub of tourism and wellness. Our proposed investment, in collaboration with our valued partners, currently stands at 250 crores INR, with the potential to scale up to 400 crores based on the support available from the government.\r\n\r\nProject Overview:\r\n\r\n1. Development Initiatives:\r\n\r\n   - 5-Star Hotel: Introducing a luxurious 5-star hotel that will provide world-class accommodations, fostering tourism and enhancing the local economy.\r\n\r\n   - Wellness Resort: Establishing a state-of-the-art wellness resort, promoting wellness tourism and positioning the region as a hub for holistic health.\r\n\r\n   - Herbs Cultivation: Cultivating medicinal herbs to promote sustainable agriculture and contribute to the region\'s biodiversity.\r\n\r\n   - Old Age Home: Creating a modern and compassionate old age home, addressing the needs of senior citizens and enriching the social fabric.\r\n\r\n2. Infrastructure Investment:\r\n\r\n   - Road and Bridge Construction: Investing in the construction of a road and bridge connecting our land to the main Rishikesh-Badrinath highway, facilitating easy access for visitors and fostering economic growth in the region.\r\n\r\nSupport Requested:\r\n\r\n1. Bridge Construction:\r\n   Seeking government support in obtaining permission to build a bridge over the Ganga, connecting our land to the main Rishikesh-Badrinath highway. This vital infrastructure will significantly enhance accessibility, enabling us to invest in the holistic development of the area.\r\n\r\n2. Land Permissions:\r\n   Kindly requesting permission to utilize land under the jurisdiction of the Irrigation Department, Forest Department, and relevant government-owned land for the access road and bridge construction.\r\n\r\n3. Single Window Clearance:\r\n   Humbly requesting a single window clearance for all necessary permissions to expedite the project, allowing prompt infrastructure development and contributing to the overall growth of the region and boosting tourism.\r\n\r\n4. Electricity Connectivity:\r\n   Additionally, seeking support to ensure adequate electricity connectivity for the proposed development, promoting sustainability and ensuring a seamless experience for residents and visitors alike.\r\n\r\n5. Capital Subsidies:\r\n   Expressing our interest in availing other capital subsidies as per the new tourism policy, contributing to the economic viability of the project and aligning with government initiatives.\r\n\r\nBenefits to the Region:\r\n\r\n1. Local Employment: The project will generate employment opportunities for local residents, fostering economic empowerment and skill development.\r\n\r\n2. Tourism & Revenue Boost: Improved accessibility will attract tourists, positively impacting the local economy and promoting Uttarakhand as a premier tourist destination.\r\n\r\n3. Sustainable Agriculture: Herb cultivation and sustainable farming practices will contribute to environmental conservation, aligning with Uttarakhand\'s commitment to ecological balance.\r\n\r\nWe are committed to investing not only in the development of infrastructure but also in the prosperity of the local community. Your support in granting necessary permissions will enable us to realize this vision.\r\n\r\nWe are optimistic about the positive impact this project can have on the region and look forward to working collaboratively with the Uttarakhand government to make this vision a reality.\r\n\r\nThank you for your time and consideration. We eagerly await the opportunity to discuss this proposal further and contribute to the growth and prosperity of Uttarakhand.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\n\r\nChirayu Magan \r\n9012011007\r\nchirayu@ecovedagreens.com\r\n', NULL, 2500000000, 'Organization', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'E', 'S', NULL, NULL, NULL, 843, 'SUBMITTED', NULL, 'N', 'N', 'Y', '2023-11-24 15:56:22', NULL, 'I', NULL, 843, 'N', 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-24 10:26:22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL),
